      "title": "## Overview",
      "content": "This plan outlines the creation of a sophisticated freelance marketplace platform, inspired by Upwork, featuring advanced verification, real-time communication, AI-assisted job management, and a portable reputation system. The platform will support diverse pricing models and robust client/freelancer metrics."
