      "content": "- **View Freelancer Listing**: Displays a list of available freelancers.\n- **View Freelancer Details**: Shows detailed profiles, including verified credentials, skills, and portfolio.\n- **View Job Listing**: Displays available job postings.\n- **View Job Details**: Shows detailed information for a specific job post.\n- **Submit Job Post**: Allows clients to create and submit new job requirements.\n- **Submit Proposal**: Allows freelancers to apply for jobs.\n- **Initiate Communication**: Enables real-time audio/video calls and chat between clients and freelancers.\n- **Use Collaborative Tools**: Access shared whiteboards and code sandboxes for project collaboration.\n- **Manage Milestones**: Create, track, and manage project milestones.\n- **Process Payments**: Facilitates secure payment transactions, including escrow and instant payout options.\n- **View Client Metrics**: Displays client ratings and performance indicators.\n- **Manage Freelancer Reputation**: Allows freelancers to export their verified achievements and reviews.",
